<div id="cover" class="center jumbotron">
  <%= image_tag('logo.png', :height =>200, :width => 200, :class=> "logo") %>
  <h2>RedRunner: Athlete Tracking App</h2>
  <br><p>Spectate athletes in real time!</p>
</div>

<div class="container" style="padding-bottom:40px;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;">
  <a class="anchor" id="about"></a>

  <div class="row">

      <h2>About</h2>
      <p class="text">
        Tired of not knowing when your athlete will run by on race day? RedRunner gives real time updates of their GPS
        location so you know when to be alert and on the lookout to cheer them on. As long as athletes carry their
        phones using our mobile app, you can see where they are simply by using our "Spectator Map" on our website!
      </p>

  </div>
</div>


<div class="container" style="margin-top:20px;">
  <a class="anchor" id="getstarted"></a>
  <h2>Get Started</h2>
  <h3>Follow 3 easy steps!</h3>
  <!-- Example row of columns -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3 style="font-weight:bold;">Athletes</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><p class="text"><span class="step">Download</span>:
            <br>Use the link below to download the Android application</p></li>
        <li><p class="text"><span class="step">Register</span>:
            <br>Open the app and follow the link to register</p></li>
        <li><p class="text"><span class="step">Start Tracking</span>:
            <br>Press the start button when the race begins</p></li>
      </ol>
      <p><a class="btn btn-danger" href="#" role="button">Download RedRunner</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6" style="border-left:1px solid #aaa">
      <h3 style="font-weight:bold;">Spectator</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><p class="text"><span class="step">Open map</span>:
            <br>Click on "Spectator Map" below or on top navigation bar</p></li>
        <li><p class="text"><span class="step">Select Race</span>:
            <br>Use the race selector on the map to choose the race</p></li>
        <li><p class="text"><span class="step">Select Athlete</span>:
            <br>Enter the athlete's bib number that you want to spectate</p></li>
      </ol>
      <p><a class="btn btn-danger" href="main" role="button" style="color:white;">Spectator Map</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="center jumbotron" style="margin-top:50px;margin-bottom:0px;padding-bottom:10px;">
  <div>
    <a style="color:white; text-decoration:underline;">admin sign in</a>
    <p style="font-size:12px;">RedRunner is a collaborative project between Red Newt Racing and a
      student project team from Cornell University.</p>
  </div>
</div>



